nts/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#format-options-numbering-system","content":"By default, NumberField displays the value using the numbering system for the user's locale. Use the `formatOptions` prop to override the numbering system by setting the Unicode numbering system locale extension."},"529":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-23","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"When focus is in the input (and the field is not read-only), keyboard behavior follows common spinbutton-style conventions:"},"530":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-24","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"**Arrow Up** / **Arrow Down** (or **Up** / **Down**): increase or decrease by `step`"},"531":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-25","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"**Page Up** / **Page Down**: larger increase or decrease when supported"},"532":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-26","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"**Home** / **End**: jump to `minValue` or `maxValue` when those props are set"},"533":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-27","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"Stepper buttons are real buttons and follow standard button keyboard activation. Use &#x2A;*`incrementAriaLabel`*&#x2A; and &#x2A;*`decrementAriaLabel`** when the default labels are not enough in your locale or UI."},"534":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-28","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"The input is associated with the visible la