"/docs/components/toggle-button-47","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Arrow Left / Right**"},"786":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-48","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Move focus between items (RAC automatically reverses in RTL)"},"787":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-49","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Space / Enter**"},"788":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-50","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Toggle the focused item"},"789":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-51","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"**Home**"},"790":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-52","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Move focus to the first item"},"791":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-53","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"**End**"},"792":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-54","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keyboard-navigation","content":"Move focus to the last item"},"793":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-55","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#aria-support","content":"`selectionMode=\"single\"` → `role=\"radiogroup\"` on container, `role=\"radio\"` + `aria-checked` per item"},"794":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-56","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#aria-support","content":"`selectionMode=\"multiple\"` → `role=\"toolbar\"` on container, `role=\"button\"` + `aria-pressed` per item"},"795":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-57","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#aria-support","content":"`aria-label` (or `aria-labelledby`) is required on the group container"},"796":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-58","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#aria-support","content":"Icon-only items require `aria-label` on each `ToggleButton`"},"797":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-59","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"✅ For grouped contextual actions — two or more closely related actions that belong together (e.g. Bold / Italic / Underline, Align Left / Center / Right)"},"798":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-60","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"✅ For compact action grouping — related actions in space-constrained layouts (e.g. Undo / Redo, Zoom In / Out / Reset)"},"799":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-61","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"✅ For multi-select scenarios — when users need to select multiple options simultaneously"},"800":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-62","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For unrelated actions that perform disconnected tasks without shared context"},"801":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-63","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For more than 5 choices — cognitive overload; consider a **Select** instead"},"802":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-64","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ When actions require strong visual distinction (e.g. Save vs. Delete)"},"803":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-65","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ When selecting an option leads to a different page or workflow — use navigation instead"},"804":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-66","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For mutually exclusive content views (e.g. Monthly / Yearly) — use **SegmentedController** instead"},"805":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-67","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keep-variants-consistent","content":"Avoid mixing different content types (text-only, icon-only, icon+text) within the same group. Mixing styles creates visual noise and makes the set feel fragmented rather than unified."},"806":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-68","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#balance-label-lengths","content":"Keep button labels of similar length. Large differences in text length cause irregular button widths and make the group appear uneven. Prefer short, concise wording."},"807":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-69","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#alignment","content":"Align the group to reflect its relationship to surrounding content:"},"808":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-70","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#alignment","content":"**Left** — when the group controls content directly below or within the same column (dashboards, tables)."},"809":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-71","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#alignment","content":"**Center** — when the group acts as a prominent toggle affecting an entire section or page."},"810":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-72","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#alignment","content":"**Right** — when the group represents utility or contextual controls (e.g. grid/list view toggle)."},"811":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-73","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#label-guidelines","content":"Use **title case**: capitalize the first letter of each word, except short prepositions."},"812":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-74","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#label-guidelines","content":"Keep labels to one or two words. Omit articles (a, an, the) and filler words."},"813":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-75","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#label-guidelines","content":"Prefer action-focused or descriptive language that communicates the option instantly."},"814":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-76","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#icon-only-items","content":"Use icon-only items only when the icon's meaning is universally recognized. Always provide an `aria-label` on each icon-only `ToggleButton`:"},"815":{"id":"/docs/components/text-field","page_id":"/docs/components/text-field","type":"page","conte